{"banner":"","content":"Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\" is now available. During this event wish, the <color=#c93f23>event-exclusive</color> 5-star characters <color=#35AACCFF>\"Emissary of Solitary Iniquity\" Wriothesley (Cryo)</color>, <color=#6957C2FF>\"Judicator of Secrets\" Cyno (Electro)</color>, and <color=#6957C2FF>\"Astute Amusement\" Yae Miko (Electro)</color>, the <color=#c93f23>event-exclusive</color> 5-star weapons <color=#bd6932>Sunny Morning Sleep-In (Catalyst)</color>, <color=#bd6932>Cashflow Supervision (Catalyst)</color>, <color=#bd6932>Staff of the Scarlet Sands (Polearm)</color>, and <color=#bd6932>Kagura's Verity (Catalyst)</color> will be available for a limited time.</P>\n<br />\n※ In most cases, the base probability of all characters and weapons is evenly distributed. If there is a boost or guarantee in effect, please refer to the corresponding rules.</P>\n<br />\n〓Rules〓</P>\n5-Star Items</P>\nFor Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\": Base probability of winning 5-star item = <color=#c93f23>0.600%</color>; consolidated probability of winning 5-star item (incl. guarantee) = <color=#c93f23>1.600%</color>; guaranteed to win 5-star item at least once per <color=#c93f23>90</color> attempts.</P>\nFor Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\", you can chart a course towards your chosen <color=#c93f23>boosted</color> 5-star character or weapon amongst all 5-star items with \"Lightrace Path.\" The choice of item will only be valid for this period of Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\".</P>\n※ When the Designated Item is a <color=#c93f23>5-Star Character</color>, the 5-star items you can obtain in the Wish are: <color=#c93f23>5-Star Characters</color>. When the Designated Item is a <color=#c93f23>5-Star Weapon</color>, the 5-star items you can obtain in the Wish are: <color=#c93f23>5-Star Weapons</color>.</P>\nWhen you obtain a 5-star item in this event wish, there is a <color=#c93f23>50.000%</color> chance it will be the Designated Item. If you obtain a 5-star item that was not your chosen item, you will receive 1 Fate Point. Once you have reached the <color=#c93f23>maximum amount</color> of Fate Points, the next 5-star item will be <color=#c93f23>guaranteed</color> to be your chosen item. Once you have obtained the chosen item, the number of Fate Points will reset to <color=#c93f23>0</color> whether or not you have reached maximum points, and you will have to accumulate them again.</P>\nAfter charting a course towards a Designated Item, you can change your choice, but doing so will reset the Fate Points to <color=#c93f23>0</color> and you will have to accumulate them again. </P>\nFor Event Wish Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\": Consolidated probability of winning the designated 5-star item (incl. guarantee) = <color=#c93f23>1.067%</color>.</P>\n※ The Fate Points for this Wish are only valid for the current period of Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\". Once the Wish event is over, the number of Fate Points will reset to <color=#c93f23>0</color>, and you will have to accumulate them again. </P>\n4-Star Items</P>\nFor Lightrace Wish \"<color=#6684ff>Heavenlit</color> Prophecy\": Base probability of winning 4-star item = <color=#c93f23>5.100%</color>; base probability of winning 4-star character = <color=#c93f23>2.550%</color>, and base probability of winning 4-star weapon = <color=#c93f23>2.550%</color>; consolidated probability (incl. guarantee) of winning 4-star item = <color=#c93f23>13.000%</color>; guaranteed to win 4-star or above item at least once per <color=#c93f23>10</color> attempts; probability of winning 4-star item through the guarantee = <color=#c93f23>99.400%</color>, and probability of winning 5-star item through the guarantee = <color=#c93f23>0.600%</color>.</P>\n<br />\n5-star weapons won in this wish come with <color=#bd6932>Masterless Starglitter</color> ×10; 4-star weapons won in this wish come with <color=#bd6932>Masterless Starglitter</color> ×2; 3-star weapons won in this wish come with <color=#a256e1>Masterless Stardust</color> ×15.</P>\n<br />\n〓Duplicate Characters〓</P>\nOn obtaining a duplicate 5-star character (whether obtained in a wish, redeemed at the shop, or awarded by the game) before 6 Stella Fortuna for that character have been obtained, the duplicate will be converted into <color=#a256e1>that character's Stella Fortuna</color> ×1 and <color=#bd6932>Masterless Starglitter</color> ×10; after 6 Stella Fortuna have been obtained, each duplicate 5-star character (whether obtained in a wish, redeemed at the shop, or awarded by the game) will be converted into <color=#bd6932>Masterless Stella Fortuna</color> ×1 and <color=#bd6932>Masterless Starglitter</color> ×25.</P>\nOn obtaining a duplicate 4-star character (whether obtained in a wish, redeemed at the shop, or awarded by the game) before 6 Stella Fortuna for that character have been obtained, the duplicate will be converted into <color=#a256e1>that character's Stella Fortuna</color> ×1 and <color=#bd6932>Masterless Starglitter</color> ×2; after 6 Stella Fortuna have been obtained, each duplicate 4-star character (whether obtained in a wish, redeemed at the shop, or awarded by the game) will be converted into <color=#bd6932>Masterless Starglitter</color> ×5.</P>\n<br />\n※ This is for \"Lightrace Wish.\" The wish guarantee count for \"Chronicled Wish\" and \"Lightrace Wish\" is shared, and is accumulated between both \"Chronicled Wish\" and \"Lightrace Wish.\" This wish guarantee count is independent of the guarantee counts of other types of wishes.</P>","date_range":"Limited-Time Event","gacha_type":500,"op_gacha_type":5001,"r3_baodi_prob":"85.400%","r3_prob":"94.300%","r3_prob_list":[{"is_up":0,"item_id":-79,"item_name":"Slingshot","item_type":"Weapon","order_value":79,"rank":3},{"is_up":0,"item_id":-80,"item_name":"Sharpshooter's Oath","it